         <abstract id="aspace_15fc74151482f7f2cd622ffdab9a3525">The materials consist of photographs documenting the Yale bicentennial celebration. Includes photographs of the decorated campus and New Haven streets, miscellaneous student groups in costume, and the Bicentennial Parade.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_ca519f5640f50056e6b7ece171056815">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 48-A (YRG 48-A), Yale pictorial records and collections.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_c93d080dec82d601c883ac1c60629648">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Yale University's Bicentennial Celebrations Photographs (RU 753). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_686c1b178b1a571e5db2752803d3ca72">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_ff7fd43f0a90398a7d1050e4e28cef86">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs documenting the Yale bicentennial celebration. Includes photographs of the decorated campus and New Haven streets, miscellaneous student groups in costume, and the Bicentennial Parade.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
